(2363, 647, 'description', 'Verizon is Moxie\'s biggest client, and for 2014, I was a part of the team that was in charge of rebuilding and refactoring their site (specifically <a href=\"http://www.verizonwireless.com\">www.verizonwireless.com</a>) for Verizon Wireless&mdash;their cell phone and wireless services sector. Since this project is a much longer term and ongoing project, it creates a different workflow that many developers are not used to&mdash;from always referencing branding and style guidelines, to getting previously built pages, widgets, and code working and interacting with new builds, to working with a huge team, to keeping up with all of the code standards that all code must strictly follow in order to be approved. Though among all these challenges, I thoroughly enjoyed working on something that is well-known and being used by so many people around the world.'),
