(835, 1, '2018-04-24 17:51:34', '2018-04-24 17:51:34', '<img src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/18836002_10158751264295627_1623195461480925977_n.jpg\" alt=\"18836002_10158751264295627_1623195461480925977_n\" />\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI was born and raised in Atlanta. I have spent the last 6 years making a name for myself in the Atlanta agency-space, and I\'m looking for my next outlet to fuel my passion for creating joyful, modern web experiences. The web has become an exciting medium over the last few years, and I am hungry to learn more as it becomes even more powerful and lucrative into the future. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nMy interests include gardening, mountaineering, music, home brewing, knitting, multimedia, and many others. I am a Maker at heart and feel most at peace when I am creating. I have spent my time in the industry learning about every aspect of the web in an attempt to turn my passion for creation into a way to make my living. My ultimate objective is to create things I am proud to show my friends and family.\r\n</p>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-24 17:51:34', '2018-04-24 17:51:34', '', 10, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
