(65, 1, '2012-12-03 17:15:18', '2012-12-03 17:15:18', 'Fall 2010: Computer Graphics is a class in which students explore the ways to create realistic models on-screen and create procedurally generated and developed graphics. All models are created purely by text. Some of the topics covered include: rendering in 3D, accurate physics modeling, advanced and dynamic geometry, working with curves, and matrix operations and transformation, just to name a few. You will need Java installed to view any of them.', 'Computer Graphics', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'computer-graphics', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:15:09', '2012-12-04 06:15:09', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=65', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2012-12-03 17:15:37', '2012-12-03 17:15:37', '<h2>Ellis Island</h2>\r\nFall 2010: Ellis Island is a research project started and currently in development at Georgia Tech as an experimental game design collaboration. The game is a massively multiplayer online game that facilitates online narrative play. The project has been run by various students over the last few years, and for one year, I helped develop 3D models in Maya to populate objects in the game. The game is set in New York City in the 1920\'s. Take a look at the project profile on Georgia Tech website <a href=\"http://www.lcc.gatech.edu/school/featuredprojects.php?id=11\">here.</a>', '3D Modeling', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3d-modeling', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:18:35', '2012-12-04 06:18:35', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=66', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(67, 1, '2012-12-03 17:16:02', '2012-12-03 17:16:02', 'I don\'t consider myself a photographer. I\'m not pursuing any sort of photography related job. Nonetheless, working in any branch of media, it\'s a good skill to have at least some sort of expertise in. You should have a trained eye for framing, composition, negative space, color, lighting, exposure, and depth of field, to name a few. So even though I don\'t specialize in photography, these skills relate very closely with Web Design, Graphic Design, and other visual media. I mainly take pictures just for the fun of it.', 'Photography', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'photography', '', '', '2012-12-12 04:29:00', '2012-12-12 04:29:00', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=67', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2012-12-03 17:16:27', '2012-12-03 17:16:27', 'I don\'t have a great hand for drawing, but I do like to take sketches that I think are cool and digitize them in my own time for fun. There\'s something about completely inked and colored drawings that I think makes them look great.', 'Illustration', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'illustration', '', '', '2012-12-04 06:20:03', '2012-12-04 06:20:03', '', 12, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?page_id=68', 0, 'page', '', 0),
