(79, 1, '2012-12-04 05:20:21', '2012-12-04 05:20:21', '<p>Our challenge for this application was to create our own paint program from scratch. The catch was that we were not allowed to use any sort of traditional painting tools. Pen, brush, line, box, were all out of the question. I decided to create a program in which the user can draw different nature scenes. His tools are elements of Mother Nature. His palette is the seasons. The application may have trouble running in your browser--you must have Java installed. If you can\'t run it, click <a title=\"Painting Nature Application\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/resources/PaintNatureApplication.zip\">here</a> to download the file to run it locally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a title=\"Painting Nature Application\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/portfolio-piece/painting-nature-application/\">Click here to try it out!</a>\r\n\r\nHere are some examples of scenes created with the program:</p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/painting-nature-1.jpg\"><img class=\"center size-full wp-image-106\" title=\"Painting Nature Nighttime Scene\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/painting-nature-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"676\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/painting-nature-2.jpg\"><img class=\"center size-full wp-image-107\" title=\"Painting Nature Springtime Scene\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/painting-nature-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" /></a>', 'Painting Nature', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'painting-nature', '', '', '2018-04-24 20:07:44', '2018-04-24 20:07:44', '', 0, 'http://jrstrauss.net/portfolio-new/?post_type=portfolio-piece&#038;p=79', 15, 'portfolio-piece', '', 0),
