(495, 1, '2012-12-16 10:17:55', '2012-12-16 10:17:55', 'This was a small assignment done in a short amount of time, thus the game\'s less polished look and feel. The assignment was designed to explore how to effectively program a cohesive and autonomous game, from registering button presses to getting images to display on the screen. The goal is to attack the randomly jittering Pikachu with the player without getting hit. The game will even run if loaded onto a physical Game Boy Advance.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n	<tr>\n		<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n			<a title=\"Title Screen\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-title.bmp\" rel=\"shadowbox[pika]\">\n				<img title=\"Title Screen\" style=\"margin: 15px auto;\" class=\"center\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-title.bmp\" alt=\"screenshot\">\n			</a>\n		</td>\n		<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n			<a title=\"Win Screen\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-win.bmp\" rel=\"shadowbox[pika]\">\n				<img title=\"Win Screen\" style=\"margin: 15px auto;\" class=\"center\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-win.bmp\" alt=\"screenshot\">\n			</a>\n		</td>\n	</tr>\n	<tr>\n		<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n			<a title=\"Fighting\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-in-game.png\" rel=\"shadowbox[pika]\">\n				<img title=\"Fighting\" style=\"margin: 15px auto;\" class=\"center\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-in-game.png\" alt=\"screenshot\">\n			</a>\n		</td>\n		<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n			<a title=\"Game Over Screen\" href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-game-over.bmp\" rel=\"shadowbox[pika]\">\n				<img title=\"Game Over Screen\" style=\"margin: 15px auto;\" class=\"center\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/pf-game-over.bmp\" alt=\"scree