(566, 1, '2013-04-30 22:52:37', '2013-04-30 22:52:37', 'Email marketing can be an extremely powerful and versatile tool when it comes to outreach and promoting business. While social media is important, email is still one of the most effective ways of both obtaining new customers, as well as keeping old ones interested. And if you know anything about the development of emails, you know that to get emails rendering correctly across hordes of email clients out there, you have to take your standards back a good decade or so (not to name any names, you know who you are). Luckily, I\'ve had some practice learning all of these tricky rules&mdash;mostly the hard way. Here are a few samples of the campaigns I\'ve helped develop.', 'Email Campaigns', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'email-campaigns', '', '', '2013-04-30 23:05:06', '2013-04-30 23:05:06', '', 12, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/?page_id=566', 0, 'page', '', 0),
