(576, 1, '2013-05-24 20:14:44', '2013-05-24 20:14:44', '<p>The Clean Show is a huge conference put on by JRiddle and Associates with over 10,000 attendees each year. The conference\'s focus is laundry and cleaning equipment: businesses from all over attend in order to preview products and equipment and decide which ones they will use for their business. JRiddle and Associates sends out a monthly bulletin to over 10,000 yearly attendees to keep them up-to-date on each year\'s upcoming show information. They have chosen SolDesign to manage these campaigns, and I have been responsible for building them out and ensuring uniformity across all email clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/clean-show-email-campaign.png\"><img class=\"add-border\" alt=\"clean-show-email-campaign\" src=\"http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/clean-show-email-campaign.png\" /></a>', 'The Clean Show', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-clean-show-bulletin', '', '', '2018-04-24 20:14:13', '2018-04-24 20:14:13', '', 0, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/?post_type=portfolio-piece&#038;p=576', 0, 'portfolio-piece', '', 0),
