r\n		<li>Georgia Institute of Technology</li>\r\n		<li>Magna Cum Laude</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</section>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n				\r\n<section class=\"skills\">\r\n	<h2>Skills</h2>\r\n					\r\n	<ul class=\"plus\">\r\n		<li>Front end: HTML5, CSS, JavaScript, Vue.js, custom UI development, UI Animation, Gulp (automated build processes), SASS, SVG, maintainability</li>\r\n		<li>Back end: C#, .Net, IIS, SQL, Apache, PHP</li>\r\n		<li>Responsive development (all devices!), mobile web optimization, cross-browser compatibility</li>\r\n		<li>Adobe Creative Suite</li>\r\n		<li>CMS: WordPress, Drupal, Sitecore</li>\r\n		<li>Knowledge of styling standards, clear and concise commenting habits, valid & semantic markup</li>\r\n		<li>Can communicate technical and creative ideas with others</li>\r\n		<li>Very high attention to detail, pixel-perfect</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n					\r\n</section>\r\n				\r\n<section class=\"experience\">\r\n	<h2>Experience</h2>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"employment\">\r\n		<div class=\"duration left desktop\">October 2014 - August 2019</div>\r\n		<div class=\"summary right\">\r\n			<div class=\"company\">Rightpoint</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">Senior Front End Developer</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">October 2014 - August 2019</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				Built custom designs from the ground up into functional experiences, set up front end architecture, created and maintained automated front end build processes, wrote modular and re-usable components, debugged inconsistencies between server environments, participated in both local and remote collaboration. Received a promotion, hired and trained junior developers, helped successfully launch 10+ enterprise web sites, and maintained many others.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"employment\">\r\n		<div class=\"duration left desktop\">August 2013 - October 2014</div>\r\n		<div class=\"summary right\">\r\n			<div class=\"company\">Engauge</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">User Experience Developer</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">August 2013 - October 2014</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				Built out sites according to design specifications using various technologies, iterated with design team to improve app quality, localized content for global clients, created custom JavaScript code for interactive microsite campaigns, and managed server deployment scripts.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"employment\">\r\n		<div class=\"duration left desktop\">May 2012 - August 2013</div>\r\n		<div class=\"summary right\">\r\n			<div class=\"company\">SolDesign Company</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">Web Developer</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">May 2012 - August 2013</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				Helped develop and maintain new and existing sites on WordPress and Drupal, managed servers to deploy code and debug issues, migrated sites to new servers, worked and communicated with clients to ensure satisfaction. \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<div class=\"employment\">\r\n		<div class=\"duration left desktop\">May 2011 - August 2012</div>\r\n		<div class=\"summary right\">\r\n			<div class=\"company\">The Children\'s School</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">Robotics Teacher</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">May 2011 - August 2012</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				Taught sixth grade technology class Robotics using Lego NXT Mindstorms and MIT\'s Scratch program to expose them to basic lessons in the fundamentals of computing and procedural programming.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"employment\">\r\n		<div class=\"duration left desktop\">August 2009 - May 2012</div>\r\n		<div class=\"summary right\">\r\n			<div class=\"company\">Institute for Computing Education</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">Summer Camp Instructor, Workshop Leader, Inventory Manager</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">August 2009 - May 2012</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				The Institute for Computing Education is a research institute funded by the National Science Foundation dedicated to raising interest in Computer Science among kids elementary through high school, especially among women and minorities. I led eight weeks of summer camps each summer, taught workshops throughout the school year, and managed their inventory throughout the year.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"awards\">\r\n	<h2>Awards &amp; Achievements</h2>\r\n	<ul class=\"plus\">\r\n		<li>Successfully completed a solo thru-hike of the 2,189 mile Appalachian Trail from Georgia to Maine 2015</li>\r\n		<li>Selected as one of Computational Media\'s \"Most Outstanding Students\" 2012</li>\r\n		<li>Dean\'s List 2008 - 2012</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</section>', 'Resume', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-20 07:04:54', '2019-08-20 07:04:54', '', 77, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/77-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
