<div class=\"company\">Institute for Computing Education</div>\r\n			<div class=\"position\">Summer Camp Instructor, Workshop Leader, Inventory Manager</div>\r\n			<div class=\"duration mobile\">August 2009 - May 2012</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-description\">\r\n				The Institute for Computing Education is a research institute funded by the National Science Foundation dedicated to raising interest in Computer Science among kids elementary through high school, especially among women and minorities. I led eight weeks of summer camps each summer, taught workshops throughout the school year, and managed their inventory throughout the year.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"awards\">\r\n	<h2>Awards &amp; Achievements</h2>\r\n	<ul class=\"plus\">\r\n		<li>Successfully completed a solo thru-hike of the 2,189 mile Appalachian Trail from Georgia to Maine 2015</li>\r\n		<li>Selected as one of Computational Media\'s \"Most Outstanding Students\" 2012</li>\r\n		<li>Dean\'s List 2008 - 2012</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</section>', 'Resume', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-20 07:02:27', '2019-08-20 07:02:27', '', 77, 'http://portfolio.jrstrauss.net/77-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
